<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT91">
<l>tamarāvar yāvarukkun tāmaraimē lāṟku</l>
<l>mamararkku māṭaravārt tāṟku mamararkaḷ</l>
<l>tāḷtā maraimalarka ḷiṭṭiṟaiñci mālvaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>tāḷtā maraiyaṭaivō meṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are His people</l>
<l rend="indent">—who, saying ‘We shall reach the black-hued [Lord]’s lotus feet’,</l>
<l rend="indent">placing flowers at [His] lotus feet and bowing down [to them] —</l>
<l>are the immortal [gods] to everyone, to [Brahmā] on the lotus,</l>
<l>to the immortals, to [Śiva] who wears dancing snakes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
